  <!-- EN: auto tesla blaster -->
  <VFE_Gun_AutoTesla.label>磁暴线圈</VFE_Gun_AutoTesla.label>
  <!-- EN: Practically part mechanoid in and of itself, the Auto-tesla is a utility turret designed to slow down a Mechanoid without it being able to adapt to the effects. Four capacitors are charged to release a bolt of electricity that is carefully modulated by the internal targeting system before release. Upon impact, the power surge affects the unit’s power module and siphons off any reserves before seeking to jump to a nearby machine, gradually weakening. This can occur twice before the initially modulated current becomes too similar to the hosts, upon which the safety overrides ground the excess power. -->
  <VFE_Gun_AutoTesla.description>该防御塔本身带有部分机械体的特征。自动线圈塔旨在不让机械体适应攻击的情况下拖慢它们的速度。内部的火控单元会用四个电容器释放出精心调制的一束电流。在击中时会在目标的电源模块中造成电涌现象，吸走储备中的所有能量，随后会跳向下一个目标。两次条约后该电流就会被机械体所完全解析，因此会被直接接地。</VFE_Gun_AutoTesla.description>
  <!-- EN: auto tesla blaster -->
  <VFE_Gun_AutoTesla.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>磁暴线圈</VFE_Gun_AutoTesla.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>
  
  <!-- EN: charge blaster turret -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoChargeBlaster.label>电荷冲击炮塔</VFE_Turret_AutoChargeBlaster.label>
  <!-- EN: A burst-fire charge turret capable of concentrating fire on nearby enemy targets at medium ranges. Unarmored targets are unlikely to survive more than a few bursts. -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoChargeBlaster.description>能够在中距离集中火力攻击附近敌方目标的突击炮塔。没有护甲的目标可经受不住它的几次连发射击。</VFE_Turret_AutoChargeBlaster.description>
  <!-- EN: Battery level -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoChargeBlaster.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelGizmoLabel>电池电量</VFE_Turret_AutoChargeBlaster.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelGizmoLabel>
  <!-- EN: Shots until out of battery -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoChargeBlaster.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelLabel>射击至电池用尽</VFE_Turret_AutoChargeBlaster.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelLabel>
  <!-- EN: Cannot shoot: Out of battery -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoChargeBlaster.comps.CompRefuelable.outOfFuelMessage>电池用尽</VFE_Turret_AutoChargeBlaster.comps.CompRefuelable.outOfFuelMessage>
  
  <!-- EN: charge lance turret -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoChargeLance.label>电荷标枪炮塔</VFE_Turret_AutoChargeLance.label>
  <!-- EN: A highly accurate, albeit slightly weaker version of the charge lance mounted on a simple-minded turret. Targets in power armor still must be cautious, as a single lucky shot is still more than capable of piercing through plasteel carapace. -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoChargeLance.description>高精度，威力稍弱的电荷标枪，安装在一个思维简单的炮塔上。即使是穿着动力装甲的人也必须谨慎对抗电荷标枪炮塔，因为一发幸运的子弹仍然有能力击穿玻璃钢护甲。</VFE_Turret_AutoChargeLance.description>
  <!-- EN: Battery level -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoChargeLance.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelGizmoLabel>电池电量</VFE_Turret_AutoChargeLance.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelGizmoLabel>
  <!-- EN: Shots until out of battery -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoChargeLance.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelLabel>射击至电池用尽</VFE_Turret_AutoChargeLance.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelLabel>
  <!-- EN: Cannot shoot: Out of battery -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoChargeLance.comps.CompRefuelable.outOfFuelMessage>电池用尽</VFE_Turret_AutoChargeLance.comps.CompRefuelable.outOfFuelMessage>
  
  <!-- EN: inferno cannon turret -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoInfernoCannon.label>地狱火加农炮塔</VFE_Turret_AutoInfernoCannon.label>
  <!-- EN: A short range cannon capable of spewing streams of fire. These turrets are usually deployed in short-ranged urban warfare. -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoInfernoCannon.description>一种能够喷出火流的短程炮。这些炮塔通常部署在短程城市战中。</VFE_Turret_AutoInfernoCannon.description>
  <!-- EN: Battery level -->
  <VFE_Turret_AutoInfernoCannon.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelGizmoLabel>电池电量</VFE_Turret_AutoInfernoCannon.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelGizmoLabel>
